Class ScalersEvioProcessor

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RecordProcessor<org.jlab.coda.jevio.EvioEvent>

    public class ScalersEvioProcessor
extends EvioEventProcessor
    This is an EVIO event processor for creating a ScalerData object from scaler bank data.
